<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - LanVision downgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - LanVision downgraded.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- McDonald &amp; Co said it downgraded LanVision Systems Inc to hold from buy.</p>
<p>-- &quot;While the underlying fundamentals that attracted us to this issue remain present, the short-term performance of the company has lagged our expectations,&quot; the brokerage said.</p>
<p>-- Said longer-term outlook for company is positive.</p>
<p>-- The stock was off one to four.</p>
</text>
